{"tid":116469,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港鐵縱火】二級燒傷命危台女張欣茹    為台灣中州科大講師","createTime":"2017-02-11T12:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T13:09:57.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16492ad30573a5e373165ceaab76c6f0d6702e92","tid":116469,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170211/large/1486814741_5cf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170211%2Flarge%2F1486814741_5cf8.jpg&h=2b164065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵昨日發生的縱火慘劇中，左邊身二級燒傷的38歲台籍女遊客，為中州科技大學觀光與休閒管理系系助理張欣茹，主要協助系主任教學與學生選課等，今年剛接講師工作，全校師生得知事件後，在社交平台Line上互通消息，並為她祈福，希望她平安渡過困境、早日康復。<br />\n<br />\n張欣茹為明道大學教學藝術研究所畢業，專長導覽解說、國際禮儀。中州科大觀光與休閒管理系主任鍾起岱指出，據知張欣茹未婚，在校服務10年，工作認真、表現良好，教學也頗受學生好評。<br />\n<br />\n校方表示，接獲消息，全校師生都相當擔心，希望她一切安好，並已協助通知家屬趕往香港。"},{"pid":"0d6c8f720fafccfb91d1292f2a360152f649cef8","tid":116469,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fd059bdac1be2b028f73774c643bd176e98867","tid":116469,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762ddc0bd2c56dd53e692736b5f11fefb607bed5","tid":116469,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:09:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}